# Phase 3: Seasonal Analysis

This folder contains seasonal water dynamics analysis.

## Four Seasons
| Season | Months | Bangla |
|--------|--------|--------|
| Pre-Monsoon | Mar-May | গ্রীষ্ম |
| Monsoon | Jun-Sep | বর্ষা |
| Post-Monsoon | Oct-Nov | শরৎ |
| Dry Season | Dec-Feb | শীত |

## Analysis
- Seasonal water extent mapping
- Inter-annual variability
- Peak flood timing

## Output
- Seasonal water maps
- Water extent time series
